# Infix `and`/`or` are binary, left-associative Call nodes (callee "and"/"or"), never a variadic
# collection: a three-term chain desugars as two nested Call nodes, per spec/grammar.md:177-178,223-224.
:a = true
:b = false
:c = true
print :a and :b
print :a or :b
print :a or :b or :c
print :a and :b and :c
